npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Bard.name = Trork Wardrummer
npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Bard.description = Tries to stay away from frontline combat, periodically buffing allies. Melee and projectiles are somewhat weak.

npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Minion.name = Trork Thief
npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Minion.description = Can use lunging attacks and sometimes dodges melee attacks. Better at melee than ranged combat.

npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Monk.name = Trork Knuckleduster
npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Monk.description = Melee attacks do more knockback, and can do slam attacks to close the distance to it's target.

