npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Slayer.name = Trork Slayer
npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Slayer.description = Aggressive and versatile, engage with caution. Occasionally uses lesser regen potions when below half health.

npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Tank.name = Trork Grunt
npcRoles.TrorkEvo_Tank.description = Slightly tougher than standard trorks, can use charge attacks.